show.description: Divorced Billionaire HeiressEnga third wedding anniversary-leye, en husband enna humiliate panni, avanoda mistress-kaga ennai veliye thalli vittuttan. Avangalukku naan power illa-nu ninaichanga—but avangalukku theriyala, naan dhan indha country-oda richest man-oda ponnu-nu. Avanoda ella wealth-um ennoda sothu dhan. Andha naale, en vazhkai-la oru powerful billionaire vandhu entry kudutharu, ellaame maathitaru. Ippo enakku dhanam irukku, power irukku, oru pudhu identity irukku. Idho, game ipo dhan start aagudhu!
